---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — HormuzWatch Strait of Hormuz Monitor" description="About HormuzWatch, the real-time Strait of Hormuz shipping disruption monitoring dashboard.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <nav class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a> <span class="mx-2">›</span> <span class="text-white">About</span>
    </nav>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About HormuzWatch</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6">
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">HormuzWatch is a real-time monitoring dashboard tracking the Strait of Hormuz shipping disruption that began on February 28, 2026. The platform aggregates publicly available data to provide logistics, trade, and energy professionals with up-to-date information on the crisis.</p>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What We Track</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-red-400">●</span><span>Strait status and vessel transit counts via AIS data</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-400">●</span><span>Live oil and energy prices (Brent, WTI, TTF, Gasoline)</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-yellow-400">●</span><span>Marine war risk insurance rates and carrier suspension status</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-blue-400">●</span><span>Diplomatic developments and peace talks progress</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-green-400">●</span><span>LNG supply disruptions and regional impact analysis</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple-400">●</span><span>Supply chain disruptions and consumer price impacts</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Data Sources</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">All data is aggregated from publicly available sources:</p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-700">
                <th class="text-left py-2 text-slate-400">Source</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 text-slate-400">Data</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 text-slate-400">Update Frequency</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-800">
              <tr><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">AISstream.io</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Live ship counts</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-400">Every 60 seconds</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">oilpriceapi.com</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Brent, WTI prices</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-400">Every 5 minutes</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Carrier websites</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Suspension status</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-400">As advisories issued</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">MarineTraffic</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Ship position verification</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-400">Manual</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">JMIC</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Maritime data</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-400">Manual</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Reuters, CNBC</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-300">Timeline events</td><td class="py-2 text-slate-400">Manual</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">License</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">All data is provided under CC BY 4.0 license. You are free to share and adapt the data with attribution. This dashboard is provided as-is for informational purposes and should not be used as the sole basis for operational or financial decisions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
